Interface EntitiesInfoStore

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EntitiesInfo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EntitiesInfoStoreImpl

    public interface EntitiesInfoStore
extends EntitiesInfo
    That interface extends EntitiesInfo(the interface for the communication structure to model) to add setters, this is very helpful for elaboration of entities during the file loading.
